oai_dc:dc.dc:title: ANNOUNCEMENTS... New AFA Executive Board Elected
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: N/A, N/A
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: After several years of preparation, the AFA is now functioning under a new table of organization. It consits of Tom Ireland, president; Clifton Witt, first vice-president; Lee Phillips, second vicepresident; financial officer to be named; and seven regional vice presidents, Tom Marshall, Northeast; Roger Kenney, Southeast; Craig Hendee, Mideast; Jim Fouts, Central; Joe McLaughlin, Western; James. H. Coffman, Northern California; Marguerite Agrella, Southern California. Helen Hanson is corporate secretary.The above officers compose the AFA Executive Board and will expedite the affairs of the AFA with wisdom and dispatch.Â
